<div class="comment" id="comment332">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20081204193701/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/4/" target="_top">匿名</a><a href="/web/20081204193701/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#medal" target="_top"><img src="/web/20081204193701im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/star_gold.png" border=0/></a><a href="/web/20081204193701/http://ja.doukaku.org/qa/#anomark" target="_top"><img src="/web/20081204193701im_/http://ja.doukaku.org/static/image/anomark.png" border=0/></a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20081204193701/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/332/">#332</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/07/08 01:12 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/07/08 01:12 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20081204193701/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/bash/">
	  Bash
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">Rating<span style="background-color: #ffdfdf;">-2/2=-1.00</span></span><a href="/web/20081204193701/http://ja.doukaku.org/5/nested/#comment332" onClick="$('#comment332 .comment_content').show()">[open]</a>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content" style="display: none">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  とりあえずこんなところでしょうか。
「指定されたフォルダ」はカレントディレクトリに置き換えてしまいました。引数で指定すべきであれば . を $1 に変更してください。ちまりに試験はしてません :-)
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre>1
2</pre></td><td class="code"><div class="highlight"><pre><span class="c">#!/bin/sh</span>
find . -name <span class="s1">&#39;*~&#39;</span> -print | xargs rm
</pre></div>
</td></tr></table>
    </div>
	

  
